title: UPDATE 3-Amazon posts second straight profit powered by Web Services
text:
UPDATE 3-Amazon posts second straight profit powered by Web Services 
Reuters Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Oct 22 (Reuters) - E-commerce company Amazon.com Inc 
on Thursday recorded a surprise profit for the second 
quarter in a row, propelled by higher sales in North America and 
its cloud computing business, and its shares rose 11 percent....
